  "detailed_description": "You find yourself stuck in a cave with nothing but your wit... and a pickaxe! As you climb your way out you'll find this is no ordinary cave.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A precision platformer designed for you to play at your own pace.<br></li><li>Fully connected map with no checkpoints. All progress made can be lost!</li></ul><br><strong>- A slightly different take on what has been coined the \"rage game\" genre.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/18a01ce41dfa70be53d2756136003345.poster.avif?t=1628641209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/18a01ce41dfa70be53d2756136003345.webm?t=1628641209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/18a01ce41dfa70be53d2756136003345.mp4?t=1628641209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>- Choose from a selection of playable characters, with more you can unlock!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/62233b596b964f30ccbfbacf1f876350.avif?t=1628641209\" width=576 height=264 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The controls are simple: You can move, jump, and use your pickaxe, that's it!<br></li><li>Master your movement to tackle all obstacles on your climb out of the cave.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "You find yourself stuck in a cave with nothing but your wit... and a pickaxe! As you climb your way out you'll find this is no ordinary cave.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A precision platformer designed for you to play at your own pace.<br></li><li>Fully connected map with no checkpoints. All progress made can be lost!</li></ul><br><strong>- A slightly different take on what has been coined the \"rage game\" genre.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/18a01ce41dfa70be53d2756136003345.poster.avif?t=1628641209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/18a01ce41dfa70be53d2756136003345.webm?t=1628641209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/18a01ce41dfa70be53d2756136003345.mp4?t=1628641209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>- Choose from a selection of playable characters, with more you can unlock!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533280/extras/62233b596b964f30ccbfbacf1f876350.avif?t=1628641209\" width=576 height=264 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The controls are simple: You can move, jump, and use your pickaxe, that's it!<br></li><li>Master your movement to tackle all obstacles on your climb out of the cave.</li></ul>",
